metadata.description:
Interactive 3D Robotic Hand is uniquely designed to give the middle finger infinitely to celebrate and remind the importance of Pride Month:

-Just be yourself
-Be fucking proud of yourself.
-Fuck everyone else.

Happy Fucking Pride Month!

Ps: Proceeds from auctions will go to organizations working to promote equality for LGBTQ+ people.
